#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kapman.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Kapman is a clone of the well known game Pac-Man."
msgstr "Kapman es un clona del ben cognoscite joco Pac-MAn."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kapman.appdata.xml:15
msgid ""
"You must run through the maze to eat all pills without being captured by a "
"ghost. By eating an energizer, Kapman gets the ability to eat ghosts for a "
"few seconds. When a stage is cleared of pills and energizer the player is "
"taken to the next stage with slightly increased game speed."
msgstr ""
"Tu debe currer trans le labyrintho per mangiar tote le pillulas sin esser "
"capturate per un phantasma.  Si on mangia un stimulator, Kapman obtene le "
"habilitate de mangiar phantasmas per alcun secundas. Quando un scena es "
"clarate de pillulas e stimulatores le jocator es portate al proxime scena "
"con un velocitate de joco legiermente  augmentate."
